## Problem
Claude `limits[]` extras filter on `entry.group !== "weekly"` only. Fixture shows `kind: "weekly_scoped"` with `group: "weekly"`. Aggregate `weekly_all` also has `group: "weekly"` and could be double-added as an extra if it appears with a model scope; currently `scopedModelSlug` may skip empty model. Worth aligning explicitly with `kind === "weekly_scoped"` per design.

## Location
contents/ui/js/QuotaParsers.js (Claude limits extras)

## Suggested fix
Prefer `kind === "weekly_scoped"` (and skip `weekly_all` / session) for parity with quotas/design.

